{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "- G\u00e9rald Darmanin, Olivier Dussopt ont fait des propositions", "start": 0.2, "duration": 2.283}, {"text": "en mati\u00e8re d'immigration.", "start": 2.483, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "La mise en place, par exemple,", "start": 3.566, "duration": 1.434}, {"text": "d'un titre de s\u00e9jour", "start": 5.0, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "pour les professions,", "start": 6.083, "duration": 1.617}, {"text": "les m\u00e9tiers qui sont en tension.", "start": 7.7, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "Et en m\u00eame temps d\u00e9cid\u00e9,", "start": 9.166, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "volont\u00e9 de durcir les fameuses", "start": 9.983, "duration": 3.117}, {"text": "obligations de quitter le territoire.", "start": 13.1, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "\u00c7a, par exemple, vous dites c'est bien,", "start": 13.966, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "on pourrait \u00eatre d'accord avec \u00e7a ?", "start": 15.566, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "- En v\u00e9rit\u00e9,", "start": 16.833, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "derri\u00e8re ce projet de loi,", "start": 17.483, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "il y a une mani\u00e8re de tenter,", "start": 18.65, "duration": 1.483}, {"text": "et de fa\u00e7on incroyablement paresseuse,", "start": 20.133, "duration": 1.783}, {"text": "de r\u00e9soudre", "start": 21.916, "duration": 0.484}, {"text": "le grand probl\u00e8me de la France aujourd'hui,", "start": 22.4, "duration": 1.866}, {"text": "qui est", "start": 24.266, "duration": 0.2}, {"text": "que nous n'arrivons plus \u00e0 travailler assez", "start": 24.466, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "pour produire ce dont nous avons besoin,", "start": 26.716, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "tout en cr\u00e9ant", "start": 28.516, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "une nouvelle fili\u00e8re d'immigration ill\u00e9gale.", "start": 29.15, "duration": 2.033}, {"text": "En fait, c'est,", "start": 31.183, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "ce que propose G\u00e9rald Darmanin et Olivier Dussopt,", "start": 32.2, "duration": 2.383}, {"text": "c'est de permettre d'augmenter", "start": 34.583, "duration": 2.75}, {"text": "les flux de migrants ill\u00e9gaux en France,", "start": 37.916, "duration": 2.934}, {"text": "pour pouvoir faire en sorte", "start": 40.85, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "que les entreprises", "start": 41.983, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "qui, aujourd'hui, n'arrivent plus \u00e0 recruter,", "start": 42.683, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "puissent compter sur cette main d'\u0153uvre ", "start": 44.333, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "bon march\u00e9 qu'on importera.", "start": 45.716, "duration": 2.217}, {"text": "D'ailleurs, cette situation, ce projet,", "start": 47.966, "duration": 2.3}, {"text": "cette strat\u00e9gie, me para\u00eet", "start": 50.666, "duration": 1.284}, {"text": "absolument irresponsable", "start": 51.95, "duration": 1.266}, {"text": "\u00e0 tout point de vue.", "start": 53.216, "duration": 0.917}, {"text": "D'abord parce qu'en France, il y a aujourd'hui", "start": 54.133, "duration": 2.5}, {"text": "5 millions de ch\u00f4meurs,", "start": 56.633, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "Guillaume Daret.", "start": 58.366, "duration": 0.417}, {"text": "5 millions ! Au sens de P\u00f4le emploi.", "start": 58.783, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "Il y a 2 millions,", "start": 60.733, "duration": 0.917}, {"text": "pr\u00e8s de 2 millions de b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiaires du RSA.", "start": 61.65, "duration": 2.483}, {"text": "Et on voudrait nous faire croire que,", "start": 64.133, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "pour pouvoir faire en sorte", "start": 65.483, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "que les entreprises fran\u00e7aises", "start": 66.716, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "trouvent des talents sur lesquels s'appuyer,", "start": 68.033, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "il faudrait qu'on aille les chercher ailleurs ?", "start": 69.733, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "Mais \u00e7a n'a aucun sens.", "start": 71.333, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Et la deuxi\u00e8me raison", "start": 72.833, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "pour laquelle", "start": 73.666, "duration": 0.334}, {"text": "c'est irresponsable,", "start": 74.0, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "c'est que les gens", "start": 74.933, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "qu'on fait venir en France,", "start": 75.65, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "ce ne sont pas seulement", "start": 77.15, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "des \"travailleurs\".", "start": 77.9, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "Ce sont des gens qui viennent", "start": 78.916, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "\u00e9videmment, et on peut le comprendre", "start": 79.883, "duration": 1.583}, {"text": "avec leur culture,", "start": 81.466, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "avec leur mode de vie,", "start": 82.633, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "avec leur vision du monde.", "start": 83.833, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "Et ceci constitue,", "start": 85.133, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "nous le voyons tr\u00e8s bien aujourd'hui,", "start": 86.15, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "la situation migratoire, ing\u00e9rable", "start": 88.25, "duration": 2.466}, {"text": "et non g\u00e9r\u00e9e depuis trop longtemps,", "start": 90.766, "duration": 2.017}, {"text": "\u00e0 laquelle notre pays est confront\u00e9,", "start": 93.05, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "cr\u00e9e toutes les tensions", "start": 94.583, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "que la soci\u00e9t\u00e9 traverse.", "start": 96.05, "duration": 1.316}, {"text": "Et c'est Monsieur", "start": 97.366, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "Delors qui le disait d\u00e9j\u00e0,", "start": 99.466, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "il y a maintenant", "start": 100.816, "duration": 0.4}, {"text": "une trentaine d'ann\u00e9es,", "start": 101.216, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "qu'aujourd'hui cette situation", "start": 102.566, "duration": 2.634}, {"text": "cr\u00e9e la rupture du pacte", "start": 105.5, "duration": 2.183}, {"text": "d\u00e9mocratique fran\u00e7ais.", "start": 107.683, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "On ne peut pas continuer comme \u00e7a.", "start": 108.616, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "La France, disait Monsieur Delors,", "start": 110.216, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "ne peut plus \u00eatre", "start": 111.516, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "une terre d'immigration.", "start": 112.316, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "Eh bien,", "start": 113.733, "duration": 0.25}, {"text": "je crois que nous avons le devoir", "start": 113.983, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "de sortir de cette logique aberrante", "start": 115.733, "duration": 2.283}, {"text": "dans laquelle Monsieur Darmanin et Monsieur Dussopt voudraient", "start": 118.25, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "nous entra\u00eener.", "start": 120.0, "duration": 0.483}]}